pesticide.PPE: Long-sleeved shirt and long pants; Shoes plus socks.

Active_Ingredients.name: Chlorantraniliprole
Active_Ingredients.mode_Of_Action: Anthranilic diamide; insect ryanodine receptor activator

Safety_Information.general_Info: When used as directed, this product does not present a hazard to humans or domestic animals.
Safety_Information.physician_Note: Have the product container or label with you when calling a poison control center or doctor or going for treatment. You may also contact 1-800-331-3148 for emergency medical treatment information.
